{"tid":1845820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[肺炎免費醫] 醫護唔罷工，即係用筆稅貼錢返工去免費醫班武漢肺炎大陸人","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:19:19.000Z","uid":63452,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c52542f7e0f621b68e3abaf49f9b8c46ad7ec903","tid":1845820,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"醫護 (最起碼隔離病房嗰班) 如果你唔罷工即係助紂為虐，幫個仆街政權不分藍黃咁害死全香港七百萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>香港衛生署確認，如「非本地居民」求診，符合武漢肺炎呈報機制，可獲豁免收費，免費醫治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGuU9fr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGuU9fr.jpg&h=86695fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: cupmedia<br />\n<br />\n原Post: <br />\n衛生署: 非本地居民如確診武漢肺炎可免費醫治<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845737\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845737</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9fe38973b01d7936bc7e55936fdc3ff2e83de8e0","tid":1845820,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"點解英國嘅實習醫生因為新contract 工時長同人工低 (同時工時長令醫療質素下降) 都可以strike，但係點解有啲香港醫護面對想全香港人中肺炎死嘅HA 同政府都可以視若無睹? 因為政府強加俾你嘅使命感? 香港醫護嘅使命感大過其他國家嘅醫護?<br />\n<br />\n你繼續唔發聲逆來順受咁幫政府無條件醫大陸人可能係滿足到你嘅使命感，但係同時係害緊全香港七百萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99261b83f87579e3096a7fa9ee41424a7b667b00","tid":1845820,"uid":61202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"所以咪撚返香港practice 啦屌你<br />\n去英國train完澳洲做不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86402a2098aea3b22a8fa9cce424a98663760bff","tid":1845820,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99261b83f87579e3096a7fa9ee41424a7b667b00","tid":1845820,"uid":61202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"所以咪撚返香港practice 啦屌你<br />\n去英國train完澳洲做不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci